Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.62,0:21:43.76,ED2J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}私　恋をしてしまった
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.49,0:21:48.81,ED2J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}ああ　瞬間風速
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.27,0:21:55.48,ED2J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}旋風のときめきにさらわれて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.68,0:21:58.66,ED2J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}雲を飛ばす
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.07,0:22:02.15,ED2J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}嵐の後
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.36,0:22:05.18,ED2J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}透き通る
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.47,0:22:08.23,ED2J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}光の粒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.68,0:22:16.17,ED2J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}混じり気のない思い　残るの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.47,0:22:18.62,ED2J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}二人でいると
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.83,0:22:20.81,ED2J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}胸が熱いね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.95,0:22:25.87,ED2J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}嘘の付けない君が好き
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.07,0:22:28.26,ED2J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}夢が破れて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.49,0:22:30.51,ED2J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}泡になっても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.62,0:22:34.66,ED2J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}後悔しない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.31,0:21:08.33,ED2C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}想一直注视着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.45,0:21:10.47,ED2C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}要一直注视着哟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.57,0:21:15.41,ED2C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}摇曳着的爱之气象图
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.81,0:21:17.88,ED2C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}两颗心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.38,0:21:20.17,ED2C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.36,0:21:24.31,ED2C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}憧憬的地方
