Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.49,0:21:48.81,ED2C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}啊　瞬间风速
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.27,0:21:55.48,ED2C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}被旋风扰动心神
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.68,0:21:58.66,ED2C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}越上云端
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.07,0:22:02.15,ED2C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}暴风雨之后
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.36,0:22:05.18,ED2C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}清澈而明净
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.47,0:22:08.23,ED2C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}光的粒粒投影
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.68,0:22:16.17,ED2C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}留下了　毫无瑕疵的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.47,0:22:18.62,ED2C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}只要两个人在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.83,0:22:20.81,ED2C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}心中就充满温暖
