Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.68,0:00:08.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好困啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.71,0:00:10.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还没到家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.36,0:00:11.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还早着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.60,0:00:12.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都是雪雪太贪心了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.99,0:00:15.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,捡栗子捡个不停才弄得这么晚的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.92,0:00:17.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是无可奈何啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.67,0:00:19.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谁叫我家是大家庭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.62,0:00:21.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋妈妈太不可靠了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.40,0:00:24.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不得不照料大家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.16,0:00:24.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.25,0:00:28.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,害怕个什么劲儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.91,0:00:30.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过是只鸟罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.50,0:00:31.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.85,0:00:38.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个羽毛是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.08,0:00:42.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.08,0:02:19.04,biaoti,NTP,0,0,0,,想找到 蓝鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.91,0:02:29.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.47,0:02:38.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.72,0:02:39.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.92,0:02:43.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,每天早上都不休息地反复挥刀  真了不起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.63,0:02:46.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是儿时养成的习惯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.09,0:02:49.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且呢  不好好练习的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.47,0:02:52.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,万一有一天能离开这个岛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.68,0:02:54.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有一个人我是无论如何都想赢的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.17,0:02:56.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.21,0:02:58.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,腋下太松垮了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.53,0:03:01.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么  我去河边洗脸了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.96,0:03:07.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.86,0:03:08.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.02,0:03:12.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是能早点回去就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.86,0:03:19.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真迟钝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.75,0:03:32.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我真是太任性了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.27,0:03:36.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然希望行人无法回去  一直留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.18,0:03:45.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.40,0:03:48.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是打得稍稍重了点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.74,0:03:49.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛好痛好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.51,0:03:51.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快点快点…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.68,0:03:52.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好啊雪乃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.31,0:03:54.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这么早要到哪去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.31,0:03:54.78,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,小铃姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.11,0:03:56.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你听我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.46,0:03:57.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不得了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.97,0:03:59.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在南边和西边的交界处
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.68,0:04:01.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了看到了 雪乃我看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.59,0:04:01.10,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.68,0:04:02.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是鸟啊  蓝色的鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.89,0:04:04.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.52,0:04:05.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个就是证据
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.20,0:04:08.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚我在南边的森岭捡栗子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.53,0:04:10.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,回家的途中不经意间看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.72,0:04:15.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是至今还没被人见到过真面目的那只传说中的蓝鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.10,0:04:17.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.82,0:04:19.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  这个是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.51,0:04:22.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有很多别的拥有蓝色羽毛的鸟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.45,0:04:25.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也有可能是绫音故意涂上色做的恶作剧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.71,0:04:26.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不会错的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.17,0:04:30.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,身为动物博士的我都没看到过的羽毛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.45,0:04:31.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不会错的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.70,0:04:32.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.80,0:04:35.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拥有这么美丽的羽毛的蓝鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.69,0:04:38.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟是什么样子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.95,0:04:41.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很想见见它并和它成为朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.25,0:04:43.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.66,0:04:46.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧  所以小铃姐你也一起帮我找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.33,0:04:47.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在就开始？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.62,0:04:48.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.67,0:04:50.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不和行人说一下的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.59,0:04:52.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,兔兔去把行人带到这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.62,0:04:53.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.32,0:04:55.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.92,0:04:57.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.56,0:04:59.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是今天还要去捡柴…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.71,0:05:00.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别管了别管了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.90,0:05:01.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,熊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.70,0:05:06.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快啊快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.56,0:05:07.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.55,0:05:17.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小铃去找蓝鸟了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.65,0:05:18.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.65,0:05:19.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,给你茶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.46,0:05:20.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.54,0:05:22.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虚幻的蓝鸟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.51,0:05:25.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,（Unidentified Mysterious Animal  未确认动物）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.51,0:05:24.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个岛上也有UMA啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.93,0:05:25.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,UMA
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.89,0:05:27.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,未被确认的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.48,0:05:30.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还未被发现的新种类的动物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.02,0:05:35.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来  对我来说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.22,0:05:38.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们也称得上是未知的珍兽了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.13,0:05:43.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是行人你不是对不可靠的事物都持否定的态度吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.24,0:05:45.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,UMA和其他的是不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.18,0:05:47.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在理论上是可以解释的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.93,0:05:48.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.25,0:05:52.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来  听说如果能抓住蓝鸟就能获得幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.90,0:05:54.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是迷信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.68,0:05:56.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是来叫行人的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.37,0:05:59.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我一会再去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.15,0:06:02.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天必须去捡柴了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.77,0:06:05.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是拿小铃没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.35,0:06:07.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然丢下了捡柴的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.42,0:06:08.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.30,0:06:10.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是雪雪硬把她带走的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.45,0:06:13.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也来帮忙捡柴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.13,0:06:13.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.90,0:06:14.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,帮了大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.72,0:06:29.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在行人正一个人捡着柴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.84,0:06:30.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  停下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.68,0:06:32.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.15,0:06:34.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看到蓝鸟的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.50,0:06:36.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,赶快开始搜索吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.30,0:06:37.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎么找呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.77,0:06:41.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是有鹰鹰和猫头鹰在就轻松多了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.39,0:06:45.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是它们昨晚就和妈妈一起去山上泡温泉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.98,0:06:47.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等我回到家的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.19,0:06:50.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只留下了「我们去温泉了」的纸条
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.38,0:06:53.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最喜欢早上睡懒觉  早上喝酒和早上泡澡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.16,0:06:56.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,简直就是一个废柴嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.44,0:06:57.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把女儿丢下不管
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.74,0:06:58.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.45,0:07:02.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话就只靠我们几个人找出蓝鸟好好地炫耀一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.16,0:07:03.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,狗狗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.41,0:07:05.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,凭借这个气味去找找看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.99,0:07:10.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.47,0:07:13.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,貌似只是羽毛进了鼻子而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.46,0:07:20.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.84,0:07:21.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.98,0:07:23.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.47,0:07:24.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为已经受潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.53,0:07:29.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天下了雨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.74,0:07:32.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说小铃  再到更深处去看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.88,0:07:35.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不对  小铃没有一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.09,0:07:43.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,回想一下的话  自从到了岛上我们大多数时间都在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.70,0:07:46.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说我给小铃添了这么多的麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.82,0:07:49.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都让她这么费心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.50,0:07:52.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我都没帮上什么忙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.40,0:07:53.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.86,0:07:55.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧走吧走吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.45,0:07:56.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.07,0:08:01.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是轻易能找到的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.07,0:08:04.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那才是所谓的虚幻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.98,0:08:09.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来  能找到蓝鸟的话就能带来幸福吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.57,0:08:11.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.39,0:08:12.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是童话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.67,0:08:13.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,童话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.03,0:08:16.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我小的时候千影姐姐经常读给我听
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.07,0:08:20.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  能带来幸福只限于童话中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.75,0:08:22.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事我当然知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.88,0:08:24.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又不是孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.32,0:08:26.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.79,0:08:29.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原来只限于童话故事中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.97,0:08:31.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.80,0:08:32.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.93,0:08:38.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,仅仅是与未知的动物交朋友这点不就足够幸福了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.75,0:08:40.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是雪雪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.23,0:08:41.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小铃姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.83,0:08:46.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是蓝鸟真的能带来幸福的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.52,0:08:48.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小铃姐想要怎样的幸福呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.54,0:08:51.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.20,0:08:59.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的话  一直维持现在的样子…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.51,0:09:01.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.70,0:09:06.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  只要大家都能健健康康的就算幸福了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.02,0:09:08.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,闻到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.90,0:09:12.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这一块的气味很重
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.47,0:09:14.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是蓝鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.21,0:09:20.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别吓到它
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.63,0:09:22.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要悄悄地接近哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.72,0:09:24.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.83,0:09:31.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,终于找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.61,0:09:33.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虚幻的蓝鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.31,0:09:42.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.26,0:09:44.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,的确是没见过的鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.34,0:09:46.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是完全都看不出是蓝颜色的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.63,0:09:47.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.42,0:09:48.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.13,0:09:49.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.94,0:09:50.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雪雪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.16,0:09:51.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.07,0:09:52.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.12,0:09:54.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,乱跑一气的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.53,0:09:55.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是会迷路的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.32,0:09:59.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  小鸟  等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.63,0:10:01.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.68,0:10:03.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,飞就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.92,0:10:05.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.38,0:10:13.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.99,0:10:23.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有深沟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.83,0:10:34.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.98,0:10:38.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.12,0:10:41.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这么晚才回来对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.83,0:10:43.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一直找不到合适的柴火…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.65,0:10:44.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.22,0:10:48.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.53,0:10:56.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小铃姐你快起来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.14,0:10:59.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.54,0:11:04.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雪乃你早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.44,0:11:06.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说早安的时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.83,0:11:07.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是悠闲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.33,0:11:10.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 我们掉到深沟里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.29,0:11:13.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都是因为雪雪暴走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.48,0:11:14.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.20,0:11:17.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真深啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.99,0:11:19.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能爬得上去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.44,0:11:20.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.22,0:11:21.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小铃姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.20,0:11:22.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,脚肿起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.27,0:11:23.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是掉下来的时候扭到的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.08,0:11:25.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来很痛的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.45,0:11:26.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.46,0:11:27.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不碍事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.14,0:11:31.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 脚是这种情况要爬上去是不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.34,0:11:32.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让我试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.47,0:11:34.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,熊熊加油
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.06,0:11:42.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,边缘太松了  不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.54,0:11:44.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,边缘比我想像的还要脆弱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.45,0:11:47.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是行人的话  在这个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.87,0:11:52.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  已经让兔兔去通知行人了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.33,0:11:55.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人应该已经察觉到我们出事了才对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.57,0:11:56.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,会来找我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.10,0:12:00.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这里可是森林的最深处
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.38,0:12:02.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是没有发现这个洞的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.25,0:12:04.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.34,0:12:05.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,炸猪排鼻子很灵敏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.97,0:12:07.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人脑袋很好使
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.38,0:12:08.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.22,0:12:11.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.79,0:12:21.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  雪乃她们没在小铃家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.43,0:12:21.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.15,0:12:23.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小铃也没回来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.27,0:12:26.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道在山里出了什么不测
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.01,0:12:29.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早知道会这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.33,0:12:32.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我就带他们一起去泡温泉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.55,0:12:33.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请冷静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.52,0:12:34.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,镜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.23,0:12:35.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么可能冷静的下来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.03,0:12:39.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果大家出了什么不测
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.17,0:12:40.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,出了什么不测  这是什么话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.67,0:12:41.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.54,0:12:43.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完全陷入混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.29,0:12:44.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,情绪变得很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.65,0:12:48.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我去山上找找
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.89,0:12:50.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,镜小姐就在村子里找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.26,0:12:52.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.77,0:12:55.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,野猪和猫头鹰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.34,0:12:57.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们去帮助行人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.92,0:13:08.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天见到蓝鸟的就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.78,0:13:09.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小铃…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.85,0:13:10.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雪乃…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.02,0:13:11.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,熊熊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.08,0:13:13.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,狗狗…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.01,0:13:15.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  不在这附近
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.19,0:13:18.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是小铃她们身边发生了什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.31,0:13:22.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.26,0:13:24.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过是在森林中迷路了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.33,0:13:26.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了炸猪排  到你出场了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.84,0:13:29.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,按照气味去寻找小铃她们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.31,0:13:31.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.23,0:13:32.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.57,0:13:36.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是小铃那边也有鼻子很灵的狗狗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.14,0:13:39.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,仅仅是因为迷路的话不会回不来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.86,0:13:42.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是遇到了什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.84,0:13:46.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.78,0:13:47.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.56,0:13:51.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天彻底黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.30,0:13:55.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.70,0:14:02.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想回家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.64,0:14:06.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.62,0:14:08.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.27,0:14:10.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.02,0:14:12.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我带了樱桃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.37,0:14:19.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我特地摘给行人和炸猪排的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.14,0:14:21.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家分着吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.82,0:14:22.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,给你熊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.29,0:14:24.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,给你狗狗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.19,0:14:25.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好好吃的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.80,0:14:26.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,给你雪乃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.72,0:14:27.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.63,0:14:28.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.77,0:14:36.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好慢啊  行人他们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.97,0:14:38.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟去哪找了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.12,0:14:43.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小铃姐你还真沉着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.52,0:14:46.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我紧张地受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.43,0:14:50.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以前也有被困在洞中的情况吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.19,0:14:54.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候行人很沉着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.30,0:14:55.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我就在想  要是我也能冷静下来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.97,0:14:57.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也会有办法的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.21,0:15:00.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小铃姐真坚强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.09,0:15:02.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是和小铃姐一起真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.31,0:15:05.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没那回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.14,0:15:08.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你什么都会做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.22,0:15:09.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又很可靠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.56,0:15:10.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,身材也好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.84,0:15:15.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且在我这个年纪已经在那个家里独自生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.93,0:15:19.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想像小铃姐那么坚强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.53,0:15:20.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好羡慕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.10,0:15:23.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的没有这回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.64,0:15:22.30,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.13,0:15:25.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.08,0:15:27.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.41,0:15:29.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的气味会被冲走的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.68,0:15:33.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.60,0:15:35.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是最糟的情况了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.23,0:15:36.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,炸猪排  野猪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.66,0:15:37.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,气味怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.72,0:15:39.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.37,0:15:42.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.29,0:15:43.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雪乃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.52,0:15:46.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.85,0:15:48.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雨声太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.28,0:15:50.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,声音似乎也传的不远
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.19,0:15:52.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.43,0:15:53.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎么找呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.22,0:16:03.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小铃现在一定是忐忑不安
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.54,0:16:07.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.77,0:16:08.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.32,0:16:10.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.18,0:16:11.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雪乃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.20,0:16:12.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,熊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.83,0:16:13.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,狗狗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.97,0:16:15.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.44,0:16:16.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.41,0:16:17.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.37,0:16:18.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.89,0:16:20.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才好像有谁在叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.70,0:16:32.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.18,0:16:36.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是你在叫我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.46,0:16:39.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.10,0:16:44.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是想让我跟着你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.62,0:16:47.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道小铃她们在哪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.70,0:16:49.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.04,0:17:02.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.76,0:17:04.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能给人带来幸福的蓝鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.88,0:17:09.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不相信这种迷信的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.35,0:17:10.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.91,0:17:12.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.36,0:17:15.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请告诉我小铃在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.18,0:17:19.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.37,0:17:21.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不会跟丢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.27,0:17:23.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.16,0:17:26.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.23,0:17:31.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.68,0:17:35.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.88,0:17:36.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.94,0:17:37.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是小铃的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.18,0:17:40.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是在那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.88,0:17:43.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小铃  雪乃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.73,0:17:44.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在里面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.19,0:17:47.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人  我们在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.34,0:17:47.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.14,0:17:49.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人来救我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.60,0:17:51.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.72,0:17:52.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.02,0:17:55.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  蓝…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.68,0:17:58.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪  到哪去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.49,0:18:00.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是幻影吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.57,0:18:03.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃  好难为情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.29,0:18:11.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一  二
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.00,0:18:15.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.84,0:18:16.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.25,0:18:19.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思  让你担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.67,0:18:22.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不得安宁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.11,0:18:24.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然会掉到那种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.80,0:18:26.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小铃也真是笨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.96,0:18:29.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛嘛  只要没事就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.40,0:18:30.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.93,0:18:32.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,凛你在做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.61,0:18:34.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了防止再有人掉下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.59,0:18:36.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想做一个栅栏之类的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.69,0:18:38.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.08,0:18:41.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都是因为这个笨蛋才让你遇到这么大的麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.10,0:18:42.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.04,0:18:45.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我要是能再小心点就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.26,0:18:48.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小铃还真是可靠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.08,0:18:50.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你也给我学着点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.55,0:18:55.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.84,0:18:58.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊呀  还真是个小鬼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.02,0:19:01.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.73,0:19:06.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不像我这样绑根安全绳的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.12,0:19:08.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是很危险的 绫音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.04,0:19:10.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为要掉下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.10,0:19:13.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里也有一个白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.87,0:19:17.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  一起吃我带来慰问大家的温泉馒头吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.93,0:19:25.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  我们也回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.46,0:19:26.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.37,0:19:29.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.17,0:19:30.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.16,0:19:32.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.10,0:19:34.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,受伤了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.10,0:19:36.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.99,0:19:38.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.60,0:19:39.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么没告诉我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.90,0:19:42.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人你生气了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.93,0:19:43.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.30,0:19:45.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让你担心真的很对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.31,0:19:47.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.63,0:19:49.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,受了伤不能隐瞒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.36,0:19:51.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别跟我这么见外啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.37,0:19:53.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都是一家人了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.43,0:20:03.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  脚很痛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.48,0:20:04.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.73,0:20:05.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是我太高兴了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.39,0:20:09.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我变得孤零零的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.06,0:20:12.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都对我很好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.97,0:20:15.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而没有一个人斥责过我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.94,0:20:20.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有  行人你说我们是一家人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.05,0:20:24.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,上来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.63,0:20:26.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我背你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.92,0:20:29.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.09,0:20:33.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.67,0:20:42.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小铃又小又轻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.59,0:20:46.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然大家都说小铃很坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.06,0:20:48.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是却不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.29,0:20:51.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小铃一直都是尽力地在勉强着
